snippet.title: How Lawyers Always Get Rappers Off
snippet.description:
Is it just us or does every Rapper get off of some serious offenses scott-free?!? (Ok not Tay-K or Shmurda or Melly no disrespect to them or anyone else, but) It's like a lawyer can get them out of ANYTHING!
